import { Box } from "@mui/material";

const Login = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      display="flex"
      justifyContent="center"
      sx={{ width: "100%", boxSizing: "border-box" }}
    >
      <Box
        display="flex"
        flexDirection="column"
        justifyContent="center"
        width="700px"
        height="700px"
        sx={{ border: "1px solid" }}
      >
        <Box sx={{ border: "1px solid" }}>Log In</Box>
        <Box component="form" sx={{ border: "1px solid" }}>
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            id="email"
            label="Email Address"
            name="email"
            autoComplete="email"
            autoFocus
          />
          <TextField
            margin="normal"
            required
            fullWidth
            name="password"
            label="Password"
            type="password"
            id="password"
            autoComplete="current-password"
          />
        </Box>
        <Box sx={{ border: "1px solid" }}>회원가입 버튼</Box>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Login;
